## Activity 启动流程

### 📌 整体流程

```
startActivity() → Instrumentation → AMS → Zygote → fork 进程 → ActivityThread → Activity.onCreate()
```

### 1️⃣ 应用层调用

```java
// 1. Activity.startActivity()
public void startActivity(Intent intent) {
    startActivityForResult(intent, -1);
}

// 2. 调用 Instrumentation
public void startActivityForResult(Intent intent, int requestCode) {
    Instrumentation.ActivityResult ar =
        mInstrumentation.execStartActivity(
            this, mMainThread.getApplicationThread(), ...
        );
}
```

### 2️⃣ Instrumentation

```java
// frameworks/base/core/java/android/app/Instrumentation.java
public ActivityResult execStartActivity(
        Context who, IBinder contextThread, IBinder token, Activity target,
        Intent intent, int requestCode, Bundle options) {

    // 获取 AMS 的 Binder 代理
    IActivityManager am = ActivityManager.getService();

    // 通过 Binder 调用 AMS.startActivity()
    int result = am.startActivity(whoThread, ...);

    // 检查结果
    checkStartActivityResult(result, intent);
}
```

### 3️⃣ ActivityManagerService (AMS)

```java
// frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/am/ActivityManagerService.java
@Override
public int startActivity(IApplicationThread caller, String callingPackage,
        Intent intent, String resolvedType, IBinder resultTo, ...) {

    return mActivityTaskManager.startActivity(caller, ...);
}
```

**ActivityTaskManagerService.startActivity()：**

```java
// frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/wm/ActivityTaskManagerService.java
int startActivity(...) {
    // 1. 创建启动请求
    ActivityStarter starter = obtainStarter(intent);

    // 2. 解析 Intent
    ResolveInfo rInfo = AppGlobals.getPackageManager().resolveIntent(intent, ...);

    // 3. 检查权限
    boolean permission = checkPermission(permission, ...);

    // 4. 创建 ActivityRecord
    ActivityRecord r = new ActivityRecord(mService, ...);

    // 5. 添加到任务栈
    mRootActivityContainer.startActivityLocked(r, ...);

    // 6. 如果进程未启动，请求 Zygote fork 进程
    if (app == null) {
        mService.startProcessLocked(r.processName, ...);
    }

    // 7. 如果进程已存在，发送启动消息
    app.thread.scheduleLaunchActivity(...);
}
```

### 4️⃣ Zygote fork 进程

**如果是新应用（进程不存在）：**

```java
// frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/am/ActivityManagerService.java
final ProcessRecord startProcessLocked(String processName, ...) {
    // 通过 Zygote 创建新进程
    Process.ProcessStartResult startResult = Process.start(
        "android.app.ActivityThread",  // 主类
        processName,                    // 进程名
        ...
    );
}

// frameworks/base/core/java/android/os/Process.java
public static ProcessStartResult start(String processClass, ...) {
    return zygoteProcess.start(processClass, ...);
}

// 通过 socket 与 Zygote 通信
private ProcessStartResult startViaZygote(String processClass, ...) {
    // 发送 fork 请求到 Zygote
    return zygoteSendArgsAndGetResult(openZygoteSocketIfNeeded(), ...);
}
```

**Zygote fork 流程：**

```
Zygote 进程 (父进程)
    │
    ├─ 读取启动参数（processClass, niceName...）
    │
    ├─ fork() 创建子进程
    │
    └─ 子进程执行：
        ├─ 关闭 Zygote 的 socket
        ├─ 设置进程名（setProcessName）
        ├─ 初始化运行时（RuntimeInit）
        ├─ 反射调用 ActivityThread.main()
        └─ 进入 ActivityThread 消息循环
```

### 5️⃣ ActivityThread

**应用进程的主线程：**

```java
// frameworks/base/core/java/android/app/ActivityThread.java
public static void main(String[] args) {
    // 1. 创建 Looper
    Looper.prepareMainLooper();

    // 2. 创建 ActivityThread
    ActivityThread thread = new ActivityThread();
    thread.attach(false, startSeq);

    // 3. 创建主线程 Handler
    if (sMainThreadHandler == null) {
        sMainThreadHandler = thread.getHandler();
    }

    // 4. 进入消息循环
    Looper.loop();
}

private void attach(boolean system, long startSeq) {
    // 获取 AMS 的 Binder 代理
    final IActivityManager mgr = ActivityManager.getService();

    // 通知 AMS 应用进程已启动
    mgr.attachApplication(mAppThread, startSeq);
}
```

### 6️⃣ AMS 通知应用启动 Activity

```java
// AMS.attachApplication()
@Override
public final void attachApplication(IApplicationThread thread, long startSeq) {
    // 获取应用进程信息
    ProcessRecord app = mProcessList.getProcessRecordLocked(...);

    // 绑定应用
    bindApplicationLocked(thread, app, ...);

    // 启动 Activity
    mStackSupervisor.attachApplicationLocked(app);
}

// 最终调用
thread.bindApplication(processName, appInfo, ...);  // 创建 Application
thread.scheduleLaunchActivity(intent, ...);          // 启动 Activity
```

### 7️⃣ ActivityThread 启动 Activity

```java
// ActivityThread.scheduleLaunchActivity()
@Override
public final void scheduleLaunchActivity(Intent intent, ...) {
    // 创建消息发送到主线程
    sendMessage(H.LAUNCH_ACTIVITY, r);
}

// 主线程 Handler 处理
class H extends Handler {
    public void handleMessage(Message msg) {
        switch (msg.what) {
            case LAUNCH_ACTIVITY: {
                handleLaunchActivity((ActivityClientRecord) msg.obj);
                break;
            }
        }
    }
}

private void handleLaunchActivity(ActivityClientRecord r) {
    // 1. 创建 Activity 实例
    Activity activity = mInstrumentation.newActivity(
        cl, r.intent.getComponent().getClassName(), r.intent
    );

    // 2. 创建 Window
    activity.attach(...);

    // 3. 调用 onCreate()
    mInstrumentation.callActivityOnCreate(activity, r.state);

    // 4. 设置可见
    r.activity = activity;
    r.stopped = true;

    // 5. 调用 onStart()
    activity.performStart();

    // 6. 创建并显示 Window
    View decor = activity.getWindow().getDecorView();
    ViewManager wm = activity.getWindowManager();
    wm.addView(decor, ...);

    // 7. 调用 onResume()
    activity.performResume();
}
```

### 8️⃣ Activity 生命周期回调

```java
// Instrumentation.callActivityOnCreate()
public void callActivityOnCreate(Activity activity, Bundle icicle) {
    // 预处理
    prePerformCreate(activity);

    // 调用 onCreate()
    activity.performCreate(icicle);

    // 后处理
    postPerformCreate(activity);
}

// Activity.performCreate()
final void performCreate(Bundle icicle) {
    // 恢复状态
    if (icicle != null) {
        onRestoreInstanceState(icicle);
    }

    // 调用 onCreate
    onCreate(icicle);

    // 分发 Fragment 生命周期
    mFragments.dispatchCreate();
}
```

### 📊 完整流程图

```
用户点击图标
    │
    ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Activity.startActivity()                     │
│ └─ Instrumentation.execStartActivity()       │
│     └─ AMS.startActivity() (Binder IPC)      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                    │
                    ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ AMS 端：                                      │
│ 1. 解析 Intent                                │
│ 2. 检查权限                                   │
│ 3. 创建 ActivityRecord                        │
│ 4. 添加到任务栈                               │
│ 5. 判断进程是否存在                            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                    │
        ┌───────────┴───────────┐
        │                       │
        ▼                       ▼
┌
